---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Nico Abramowski">
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[1fr_320px] items-start">
    <section class="card p-7 reveal">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">About me</h1>

      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        I’m Nico Abramowski, a B.Sc. Computer Science candidate at the University of Rostock. I’m building a career in
        data warehousing and analytics engineering, with a focus on clear dimensional models, reliable ELT pipelines,
        and concise documentation.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Focus areas</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li><strong>Modeling:</strong> Kimball-style dims/facts, SCD strategies, pragmatic naming and testing.</li>
        <li><strong>ELT & Orchestration:</strong> <em>dbt</em> for transformations; Airflow/Prefect (foundational); idempotent, incremental loads.</li>
        <li><strong>Data quality:</strong> Expectations and basic data contracts that prevent regressions.</li>
        <li><strong>Delivery:</strong> Lightweight dashboards and docs that answer a specific business question.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Toolbox</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li><strong>SQL & Warehouses:</strong> PostgreSQL, DuckDB.</li>
        <li><strong>Transformation:</strong> dbt.</li>
        <li><strong>Python:</strong> pandas, small ETL/ELT utilities.</li>
        <li><strong>Platform:</strong> Docker, Git, Linux (Mint).</li>
        <li><strong>Streaming (intro):</strong> Kafka/Debezium.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Background</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        Prior work included Linux networking (TSN/SDN) and scripting, which shaped my bias toward reliability,
        repeatability, and simple designs.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">What I’m looking for</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        Entry-level roles in data warehousing / analytics engineering. I enjoy shipping clean models, automated
        transformations with tests, and straightforward dashboards. Remote-friendly teams are a plus.
      </p>
    </section>

    <aside class="card p-7 reveal" style="transition-delay:.05s">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Contact</h2>
      <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        <div>Email: <a class="underline" href="mailto:nico.abramowski01@gmail.com">nico.abramowski01@gmail.com</a></div>
        <div>GitHub: <a class="underline" href="https://github.com/Nico-Ab" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Nico-Ab</a></div>
        <div>LinkedIn: <a class="underline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nico-abramowski-0aa460383" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">nico-abramowski-0aa460383</a></div>
        <div>CV: <a class="underline" href={`${base}CV.pdf`} download>Download PDF</a></div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
